license: "MIT"
keywords:
  - negative results
  - publication bias
  - open science
  - medicine
  - clinical trials
  - dark data
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-01-01"
abstract: >
  An open, structured, and freely accessible registry of negative and null
  results in medical and biomedical research, intended to reduce duplicated
  effort caused by publication bias. Entries follow a standardized JSON
  schema and are validated automatically. Individual data entries carry
  their own license (see the DATA LICENSING section of README.md).
